-- Citi plans to add 200 new U.S. branches
-- 
-- Fri Apr 15, 2011 10:34pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/16/us-citigroup-branches-idUSTRE73E8DI20110416

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Citigroup Inc ( C.N ) is planning to add 200 U.S. branches over the next three years and may expand into Seattle and Atlanta, a spokesman confirmed on Friday. 

 The lender plans to add about 100 branches in California and New York, and another 100 elsewhere in the country by the end of 2013, according to Citigroup spokesman Sean Kevelighan. The expansion was first reported by Bloomberg News. (Reporting by  Paritosh Bansal ; editing by  Andre Grenon )